&lt;p&gt;Gemini is seeking a highly experienced Institutional Sales &amp;amp; OTC Senior Principal to own and grow our institutional OTC and broader execution business. This individual will sit at the center of Gemini’s institutional revenue engine, responsible for driving OTC trading flow, expanding institutional relationships, and ensuring seamless execution across spot, derivatives, and structured flows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;This role is required to be in person twice a week at our New York City, NY office.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
