&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Originate, onboard, and grow institutional OTC relationships across hedge funds, prop trading firms, asset managers, family offices, and crypto-native institutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive spot, derivatives, and structured flow through Gemini’s OTC platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain high-touch coverage of key institutional clients, providing market color, trade ideas, and risk-aware execution strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Trading to improve spreads, liquidity depth, and overall execution quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and develop new institutional revenue opportunities across OTC, custody, staking, and derivatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and expand strategic partnerships across funds, intermediaries, fintechs, and crypto-native ecosystems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Gemini in institutional sales cycles, client engagements, and industry conferences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Capture and synthesize client feedback to inform Trading and Product improvements across execution and infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and help shape institutional go-to-market strategy across OTC and adjacent product lines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;12+ years of experience in institutional sales, OTC trading, or execution roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong track record of generating meaningful institutional trading volume and revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep existing relationships across hedge funds, prop trading firms, family offices, asset managers, and crypto-native institutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of OTC market structure, liquidity dynamics, derivatives, and execution workflows&lt;/li&gt;
